![Burning163.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1612201541663-1D0Q90VUOUP1RM4GNYYM/Burning163.jpg)

It was supposed to be the start of a new generation of heroes. It was supposed to be the last grasp at greatness for a franchise on it’s last legs. It was supposed to come out 4 separate times over the last 4 years. That’s right, this week we are talking **The New Mutants** in a full recap and review! The long-awaited, and incredibly frustrating entry in the Fox X-Men universe left many scratching their heads, but what did the guys at CBC think? Join us as we talk bears, buffalo wings and more BS than usual in this last trip through the land of mutants before they debut in the MCU!

